    diagrams[1]:
      - "flowchart LR\n  subgraph App\n    Characters\n    Character\n    ItemSearch[\"Item Search\"]\n    ItemLevel[\"Item Level Average\"]\n    Inventory\n    CoreData[\"Core Data\"]\n  end\n\n  Website[\"Item Dictionary\\n(Web)\"]\n  Xlsx[\"Xlsx\"]\n\n  Xlsx -->|Bundle| Characters\n  Characters -->|Select| Character\n  Character --> Inventory\n  Inventory -->|Search| ItemSearch\n  Website -->|Crawling| ItemSearch\n  ItemSearch -->|Select| Inventory\n  Inventory --> ItemLevel\n  Character -->|Save| CoreData"
